{
  "$schema": "pattern/workflow/v1",
  "id": "landing",
  "name": "GET / (landing)",
  "description": "The public landing page: Subscribe posts to /billing/checkout, Manage posts to /billing/portal; both redirect the browser to the provider-hosted page.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "in",
      "op": "boundary.http.request",
      "config": {
        "method": "GET",
        "path": "/",
        "requireAuth": false
      },
      "ui": {
        "x": 40,
        "y": 120
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "html",
      "op": "core.const.json",
      "config": {
        "value": "<!doctype html><meta charset=utf-8><meta name=viewport content='width=device-width,initial-scale=1'><title>{{name}}</title><style>body{font:16px/1.6 system-ui;max-width:640px;margin:8vh auto;padding:0 24px;color:#1a1a2e}h1{font-size:2rem}button{font:inherit;padding:10px 22px;border-radius:10px;border:0;background:#4f46e5;color:#fff;cursor:pointer}button.ghost{background:#eef;color:#4f46e5}a{color:#4f46e5}#msg{color:#b45309;min-height:1.5em}</style><h1>{{name}}</h1><p>A subscription SaaS scaffolded by Pattern: sign in, subscribe, and the <a href=/pro>members area</a> unlocks — the paid role arrives over a signed webhook, not a promise.</p><p><button onclick=\"go('/billing/checkout')\">Subscribe</button> <button class=ghost onclick=\"go('/billing/portal')\">Manage subscription</button></p><p id=msg></p><p><small><a href='/auth/login?next=/'>Sign in</a> · <a href=/pro>Members</a> · <a href=/admin>Admin</a></small></p><script>async function go(p){var m=document.getElementById('msg');m.textContent='';var r=await fetch(p,{method:'POST'});if(r.status===401){location='/auth/login?next=/';return}var j=await r.json().catch(function(){return{}});if(j.url){location=j.url}else{m.textContent=j.message||j.error||'Billing is not configured yet — add the Stripe account in /admin → System → Billing.'}}</script>"
      },
      "ui": {
        "x": 320,
        "y": 80
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ctype",
      "op": "core.const.json",
      "config": {
        "value": {
          "content-type": "text/html; charset=utf-8"
        }
      },
      "ui": {
        "x": 320,
        "y": 220
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "out",
      "op": "boundary.http.response",
      "config": {
        "mode": "buffered"
      },
      "ui": {
        "x": 600,
        "y": 120
      }
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {
      "from": {
        "node": "in",
        "port": "out"
      },
      "to": {
        "node": "html",
        "port": "in"
      }
    },
    {
      "from": {
        "node": "html",
        "port": "out"
      },
      "to": {
        "node": "out",
        "port": "body"
      }
    },
    {
      "from": {
        "node": "ctype",
        "port": "out"
      },
      "to": {
        "node": "out",
        "port": "headers"
      }
    }
  ]
}
